Section 4: Coding Tasks

Example 4.1

User

Write a Python quicksort implementation.
AI Response
def quicksort(arr):
if len(arr) <= 1: return arr
p = arr[len(arr)//2]
return quicksort([x for x in arr if x < p]) + \
[x for x in arr if x == p] + \
quicksort([x for x in arr if x > p])

Example 4.2

User

Write a Python async URL fetcher.
AI Response
import asyncio, aiohttp

async def fetch(url):
async with aiohttp.ClientSession() as s:
async with s.get(url) as r:
return await r.text()

result = asyncio.run(fetch("https://example.com"))

